Future Features
===============

V (builtin) default selection
V (builtin) return objects instead of menu names
V (plugin) filtering by typing
V (plugin) inner headlines (for gitter) with filtering
V micro menu (for yes/no choices)
V (plugin) ANSI colored menu items
* (builtin) backward compatible show_menu
* (builtin) limit size (to terminal width / height)
* (plugin) readline-style editing on the filtering line
* (derived) multi column display (for file menu and gitter)
* (plugin) shorten long ANSI-colored lines to specific width

